Package: webterminal
Title: Fast Browser-Based Terminal for 'RStudio Server'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Sondre Nærø", "Skarsten",
           email = "Sondre.Naro.Skarsten@dnb.no",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Opens a browser-based terminal inside the 'RStudio Server'
    viewer pane by forwarding to a locally running 'ttyd' or 'shellinabox'
    daemon and an optional 'tmux' session. The package does not install or
    modify any system software; it only locates user-installed helper
    binaries, manages daemon lifecycle, and proxies through 'RStudio
    Server' built-in localhost URL proxy via 'rstudioapi'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
OS_type: unix
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    tools,
    utils,
    rstudioapi (>= 0.11)
Suggests:
    cli (>= 3.6.0),
    httpuv,
    spelling,
    testthat (>= 3.2.0),
    withr
SystemRequirements: 'ttyd' (>= 1.7) or 'shellinaboxd' (>= 2.21); 'tmux';
    iproute2 ('ss'); bash
URL: https://github.com/sondreskarsten/webterminal
